highlights.text: “Shape of You” by Ed Sheeran has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 181 weeks straight.
“Banana (feat. Shaggy) - DJ FLe - Minisiren Remix” by Conkarah, Shaggy, and DJ Fle is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 59 spots at #100.
Bad Bunny has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “Hasta Que Dios Diga” is the highest at #37.
“Stay Gold” by BTS is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #72.
